## Queries

Having all entities be made out of components allows us to make queries to find specific kinds of entities that match our requested mix of components.

For example, you can use this simple query to get all buildings that are abandoned:

```
public partial class MySystem : GameSystemBase
{
	protected override void OnCreate()
	{
 base. OnCreate();

m_Query = GetEntityQuery(ComponentType. ReadOnly<Building>(), ComponentType. ReadOnly<Abandoned>());
	}
}

```

Check out thequeries guidefor more information about them.

