### In C# code (when you don't have a choice)

Sometimes, you still need to translate a string in C#, because you have no UI mod or because it's outside of the UI mod's realm.

The game assemblies do not provide any shortcut to get a key's translation, so let's get started by creating two little extension methods that will ease our job, one of which leveraging. NET's String. Formatto support variables interpolation.

```
